lead_paragraph: When the Miami Dolphins made a goal-line tackle on the final play to seal their latest victory, quarterback Ryan Tannehill sprinted onto the field, leaped to chest-bump a teammate and then sprawled happily to the turf.

headline.print_headline: Dolphins Win 6th in a Row by Beating Niners 31-24
